===Etymology===
The horses' coat-color {{zh-l|*鸝}} is possibly related to the birds' color {{zh-l|*鸝}}.

{{zh-ref|Schuessler (2009)}} minimally reconstructs {{och-l|驪|tr= {{IPAfont|*rê ~ re}}}}, which he relates to {{och-l|盧|tr= {{IPAfont|*râ}}}} (minimally reconstructed) by pointing out the vowel alternation {{IPAfont|*a}} vs. {{IPAfont|*e ~ i}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

See {{zh-l|*盧}} for more.

